title: Week 6 NFL Recap, Analysis; Are the 49ers legit? (Football 10/14)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap all the Week 6 Sunday action from around the NFL. The guys discuss all 12 games on the Sunday slate including Texans-Chiefs (2:00), 49ers-Rams (15:27), Steelers-Chargers (30:37), Eagles-Vikings (43:50), Cowboys-Jets (53:05), Seahawks-Browns (1:03:44), Falcons-Cardinals (1:13:35), Panthers-Buccaneers (1:19:30), Saints-Jaguars (1:25:51), Titans-Broncos (1:31:13), Redskins-Dolphins (1:34:56), and Bengals-Ravens (1:40:17).
